column5: Hello  Got tuesday off again and looking to go fishing,  If anyone  would like to fish for either whitties and lakers or perch again....     Or pike and Crappie at a little lake I know that is full of fish...  Clampet let me know if your available again..  Willing to pay for the expences gas, bait etc etc...   I dont have the car on Tuesday so if you would like to fish anywhere let me know please..  Dave  (416)531-4432
Give me a call at the store  (416)651-6436  Dave
